<s docid="FBIS3-43040" num="188"> In addition, the state of Pennsylvania is conducting a project to activate used rubber so as to chemically bind it with plastics for the purpose of transforming old rubber into a polymeric composite material suitable for manufacturing hoses, gaskets, rollers, and even new tires.</s>

