<s docid="FBIS3-43040" num="190"> Calculations performed at the NIID indicate that more than 90 percent of wastes may be reprocessed and used in the interests of the national economy.</s>

<s docid="FBIS3-43040" num="191"> Ninety percent of wastes from the sawmilling and woodworking industry are used, as are 98 percent of polystyrene wastes.</s>

