<s docid="FBIS3-43040" num="219"> At the Rybinsk Motor Building Production Association, the economic impact from the introduction of this process has amounted to 462,000 rubles a year (in 1991 prices).</s>

<s docid="FBIS3-43040" num="220"> Several hundreds of tons of tungsten- and cobalt-containing wastes is generated each year at the subsector's enterprises during the process of pointing and using hard-alloy cutting tools.</s>

