<s docid="FBIS3-24648" num="16"> Automotive Industry (Italy) A hydrogen-fueled engine developed by the Agency for New Technologies, Energy, and the Environment (ENEA) and VM Motori, in collaboration with Magneti MareIIi and the University of Pisa, is currently being tested on a Fiat van.</s>

