<s docid="FBIS3-24648" num="43"> Located in the Ngari District of western Xizang, the Gerze solar power station, for which construction costs totaled some 2.5 million yuan ($287,000), is a joint investment project involving the Ministry of Electric Power, the Xizang Planning Commission and Gerze County.</s>

<s docid="FBIS3-24648" num="44"> Ground was broken on the project in 1991 and the facility was officially inaugurated in November 1993.</s>

