<s docid="FBIS3-24648" num="277"> Stephen M. 733-6343 JAPAN: LOW-POLLUTION VEHICLES Japanese industries, backed by government financing, are promoting the development and marketing of low-pollution vehicles.</s>

<s docid="FBIS3-24648" num="278"> Japanese automobile manufacturers and electric power and gas companies have been cooperating in government-backed efforts to promote the development and sale of low-pollution automobiles, including those that use natural gas, hydrogen, methanol, solar power, electric batteries and combinations of these as energy sources.</s>

